---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Getting Started // AetherIndex Foundry</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-[#02040a] text-white font-sans selection:bg-blue-500/30">
		<nav class="border-b border-white/5 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-xl sticky top-0 z-50">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
				<a href="/" class="font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase italic text-lg text-white">Aether<span class="text-blue-500">Index</span></a>
				<a href="/" class="text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">← Back to Foundry</a>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
			<div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-full bg-blue-500/5 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-8">
				The_Newbie_Path_v1.0
			</div>
			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-12 uppercase italic leading-none">
				Your First <span class="text-blue-500">Steps.</span>
			</h1>

			<div class="space-y-16">
				<section class="relative pl-12 border-l border-white/10">
					<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-blue-600 border-4 border-[#02040a]"></div>
					<h2 class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400 mb-4">Step_01: The Logic Foundation</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">Before touching AI, you must speak the language of logic. AI is built on Python and Mathematics.</p>
					<div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors">
						<h3 class="font-bold mb-2 uppercase italic text-sm">Recommended Resource:</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4">"30 Days of Python" & "Mathematics for ML" in our Foundations sector.</p>
						<a href="/?search=python" class="text-[10px] font-mono text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest">View in Manifest →</a>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="relative pl-12 border-l border-white/10">
					<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-800 border-4 border-[#02040a]"></div>
					<h2 class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400 mb-4">Step_02: Grocking Transformers</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">Learn the "Engine" of the current AI revolution. You need to understand how words turn into vectors.</p>
					<div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors">
						<h3 class="font-bold mb-2 uppercase italic text-sm">Recommended Resource:</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4">Andrej Karpathy's "Zero to Hero" series. This is the gold standard.</p>
						<a href="/?search=karpathy" class="text-[10px] font-mono text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest">View in Manifest →</a>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="relative pl-12 border-l border-white/10">
					<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-800 border-4 border-[#02040a]"></div>
					<h2 class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400 mb-4">Step_03: Prompt Engineering</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">Mastering the interface. Learn how to design system prompts and control LLM behavior effectively.</p>
					<div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors">
						<h3 class="font-bold mb-2 uppercase italic text-sm">Recommended Resource:</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4">DAIR.AI's "Prompt Engineering Guide."</p>
						<a href="/?search=prompt" class="text-[10px] font-mono text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest">View in Manifest →</a>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="relative pl-12 border-l border-white/10">
					<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-800 border-4 border-[#02040a]"></div>
					<h2 class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400 mb-4">Step_04: Your First Agent</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">Stop chatting and start building. Create a system that uses tools (Search, Calculator, API) to solve problems.</p>
					<div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors">
						<h3 class="font-bold mb-2 uppercase italic text-sm">Recommended Resource:</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4">"Generative AI for Beginners" by Microsoft.</p>
						<a href="/?search=microsoft" class="text-[10px] font-mono text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest">View in Manifest →</a>
					</div>
				</section>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-32 p-12 rounded-3xl border border-blue-500/20 bg-blue-500/5 text-center">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase italic mb-4">Ready to Explore?</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-8">The Foundry contains 100+ more specialized gems including RAG, MLOps, and Infrastructure.</p>
				<a href="/" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase text-xs transition-all">Launch Full Manifest</a>
			</div>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>